{"tid":2506444,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋game]有無巴絲十幾年前玩過呢隻PSP game","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T07:25:52.000Z","uid":352409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f548522df774ce2111634f90eca10abf8e95ca04","tid":2506444,"uid":352409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"八到九歲個陣我玩過隻psp game遊戲機制好有趣，但因為係日文搵唔番個遊戲..<br />\n求下你地睇下有無辦法搵番我童年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻game是咁的:<br />\nrpg升lv打怪,日文字(應該係日本game黎?)<br />\n遇怪後會入左個場景,主角可以跑黎跑去,一路風箏隻怪一路用魔法<br />\n入面有隻拎住掃把既粉紅色女法師可以召喚水龍捲同火球術打啲怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個遊戲機制好特別，唔係回合制，<br />\n好少game係2006-2008年出有類似依家啲傳說對決咁既機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n好想搵番個隻game，睇番個隻game既中文攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57d6905c2057e7728a0a515edfe66ed9fe6e828","tid":2506444,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"多D  HINTS啦"},{"pid":"8d8c3c56cae87c6c1519423a05c9084a9cae3be4","tid":2506444,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"2d?3d? <br />\nQ版?寫實?<br />\n主角女主角乜造型?"},{"pid":"7d6cb7489d41e360b3508007d2f63f08ec6eec52","tid":2506444,"uid":352409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d8c3c56cae87c6c1519423a05c9084a9cae3be4","tid":2506444,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"2d?3d? <br />\nQ版?寫實?<br />\n主角女主角乜造型?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"算係3D, 有立體感, 係卡通feel<br />\n主角係可以自己整造型,可以整唔同髮色同髮型<br />\n好似可以揀唔同職業 好似玩過 僧/法師<br />\n記得有個場景係綠色，行黎行去都係一樣,最後唔識過灰心到DEL左game去down左sd高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkg